race.comment: SNOWY RULES (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (30.44) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can make amends this time. ALL THE CASH (1) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at Nowra over 365m behind Mount Fuji (21.68) in a Grade 4/5. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from six starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. I'M BETTER (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (18.54) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Better than last start and can bounce back. KAVA QUEEN (7) cannot be underestimated.
